      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>chopped tomatoes </strong>and<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong>, then increase the heat to medium and stir</p><p>Cook for 10-15 min until the tomatoes have reduced to the consistency of a thick sauce – this is your<strong> tomato sauce</strong></p>",
